{"tid":2133761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"行政長官會晤國安委 懶理疫情嚴峻形勢","createTime":"2020-07-31T09:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T09:45:05.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"415983902c7783ad8806b4060542a8181e48a916","tid":2133761,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"駐港國安公署與國安委舉行 首次工作會晤<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-07-31 17:05<br />\n<br />\n中央駐港國安公署今日與香港特區維護國家安全委員會，舉行首次工作會晤，討論自《港區國安法》生效以來的落實執行工作，並就有關事項交換意見。國安委主席、行政長官林鄭月娥率領全體國安委成員出席會議，國家安全事務顧問駱惠寧、駐港國安公署署長鄭雁雄、駐港國安公署副署長李江舟和孫青野亦有出席。<br />\n<br />\n根據《港區國安法》第53條，駐港國安公署應當與國安委建立協調機制，以及在工作層面與特區維護國家安全的有關機關建立協作機制，加強信息共享和行動配合。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2349964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2349964&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1w2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=a655884f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2349964</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9AcxwN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9AcxwN.jpg&h=70cb4167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4a68ee86f55236b1f170719c67662559cdeaadc","tid":2133761,"uid":5943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"又唔撚戴口罩<br />\n正仆街"},{"pid":"82ac43b26e372b2a3d5e40ebd1094ac39a722b44","tid":2133761,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"搵條友咳,一鑊熟咪幾好"},{"pid":"dc4b3258ff3be88cbf145c2d3c8bd8ea3d02316b","tid":2133761,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"劏房波雙手咩事？<br />\n唔識規矩？"},{"pid":"f3a6f7aa565a7057524266cab034a3aff412072e","tid":2133761,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc4b3258ff3be88cbf145c2d3c8bd8ea3d02316b","tid":2133761,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"劏房波雙手咩事？<br />\n唔識規